Class Simulate

  • java.lang.Object
    • Simulate

  • public class Simulate
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates an integer array of size 100 filled with random values between 0 and 100, prints the unsorted array out to the console, sorts the array using dual pivot quicksort, and prints the sorted array out the console.
